### Login to get token (Tour Operator)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "operator@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login to get token (Tour Guide)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "guide@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Test Authentication (any authenticated user)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/TourGuideAssignment/test-auth
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get All Tour Guide Assignments (Tour Operator only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/TourGuideAssignment
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get All Tour Guide Assignments with filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/TourGuideAssignment?TourId=1&IsActive=true&PageNumber=1&PageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get All Tour Guide Assignments by Tour Guide ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/TourGuideAssignment?TourGuideId=1&PageNumber=1&PageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get All Tour Guide Assignments by Booking ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/TourGuideAssignment?BookingId=1&PageNumber=1&PageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get All Tour Guide Assignments by Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/TourGuideAssignment?AssignedDateFrom=2024-01-01&AssignedDateTo=2024-12-31&PageNumber=1&PageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Lead Guide Assignments only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/TourGuideAssignment?IsLeadGuide=true&PageNumber=1&PageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get My Assignments (Tour Guide only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/TourGuideAssignment/my-assignments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Create New Tour Guide Assignment
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/TourGuideAssignment
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "TourId": 1,
  "BookingId": 1,
  "TourGuideId": 1,
  "AssignedDate": "2024-01-15T00:00:00",
  "IsLeadGuide": true
} 